## Undefined behavior & performance

UB:
{{ub_section}}

Performance:

- Profilers worth wiring: Tracy (in-process), VTune (Intel), perf (Linux).
  `luban setup --with tracy` puts Tracy on PATH if you want it.
- Hot-path watch list: allocations in inner loops, `std::vector` repeated
  growth, false sharing across threads, virtual dispatch in tight loops.
- For profileable Release: add `-O2 -fno-omit-frame-pointer` (or the
  cmake equivalent) — `-O3` plus aggressive inlining makes flame graphs
  unreadable.
